### Audit health - public
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health

### List current tenant audit events - direct service
GET http://localhost:8082/api/audit-events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
X-Request-Id: audit-direct-001

### Get one audit event by eventId - direct service
GET http://localhost:8082/api/audit-events/<EVENT_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
X-Request-Id: audit-direct-002

### List current tenant audit events - through Kong
GET http://localhost:18000/api/audit-events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
X-Request-Id: audit-kong-001

### Missing token through Kong - expected 401
GET http://localhost:18000/api/audit-events
X-Request-Id: audit-kong-missing-token
